{
  "name": "Tornado",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/air/wind-tornado-cyclone-white.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>You create a 6 Space high, 2 Space diameter Cylinder of swirling winds within range for the duration. Creatures in the area are Slowed 2, Blinded, and Fully Concealed.</p><p>When a creature enters the area for the first time on its turn or starts its turn there, it makes a Might Save against your Save DC. </p><ul><li><p><strong>Save</strong> <strong>Failure:</strong> They are pushed 1 Space horizontally in a random direction.</p></li><li><p><strong>Failure (each 5):</strong> They are pushed 1 additional Space.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Spell Cast:</strong> When you cast the Spell, make a Spell Check against the Might Save of each target in the area.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Save Failure:</strong> They are pushed 1 Space horizontally in a random direction.</p></li><li><p><strong>Failure (each 5):</strong> They are pushed 1 additional Space.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Moving the Cylinder:</strong> When you Sustain this Spell or by spending 1 AP, you can move the Cylinder up to 5 spaces to another Space within range.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP, Repeatable) </strong>The range of the Spell increases by 5 Spaces. You can use this Enhancement a maximum of two times.</p><p><strong>Area: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The diameter of the Cylinder increases by 1 Space and the height increases by 3 Spaces.</p><p><strong>Increased Push : (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> The distance pushed increases by 1 Space.</p><p><strong>Vortex: (1 MP)</strong> When you cast the Spell, creatures within the area, or within 1 Space of the area, make a Might Save against your Spell Check. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> They are pulled toward the Point of Origin.</p><p><strong>Storm Core: (1 MP, Repeatable)</strong> A creature that fails its Save also takes 1 Lightning damage.</p><p><strong>Updraft: (2 MP, Repeatable)</strong> A creature that fails its Save is also pulled upward 3 Spaces.</p>",
